---
title: Italian-Style Steak Sandwiches with Sautéed Peppers and Spinach Salad
description: Sweet caramelized onions and peppers top this juicy balsamic-drizzled steak sammie. We've paired it with a classic spinach salad for a crunchy, crisp and healthy finish!
